rows.label: tlk41400072_02_msg0001
rows.name:
If it weren't for Blades, we would all be
able to live here in Gula in peace.

rows.label: tlk41400072_02_msg0002
rows.name:
And yet, perhaps then I wouldn't
be here today...

rows.label: tlk41400072_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I slipped on the outer wall the
other day and fell onto the
back of the Acedian Divine Beast.

rows.label: tlk41400072_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I cried for help, but no one seemed to
notice my absence. I thought that was
it for me, but then a Blade saved me.

rows.label: tlk41400072_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I know it's not the Blades we should
be blaming, it's the ones in control
of them...but still...
